Comment: 0,0:00:00.93,0:00:00.93,Comment,,0,0,0,,——Text——
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.47,0:00:35.84,Default,,0,0,0,,如果要下的话  倒是希望能在早上就开始下
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.57,0:02:14.69,Default,,0,0,0,,伊万莉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.78,0:02:18.36,Default,,0,0,0,,宇佐
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.45,0:02:19.36,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.24,0:02:22.53,Default,,0,0,0,,没什么  只是觉得雨下得很大
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.91,0:02:24.49,Default,,0,0,0,,难道你没带伞吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.12,0:02:28.08,Default,,0,0,0,,是我疏忽大意了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.00,0:02:30.21,Default,,0,0,0,,要我借你吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.25,0:02:32.50,Default,,0,0,0,,借给我  你用什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.80,0:02:35.84,Default,,0,0,0,,难道你是二刀流?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.88,0:02:36.88,Default,,0,0,0,,我只带了一把伞
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.72,0:02:40.93,Default,,0,0,0,,我还要帮老师做事  所以暂时还不回去
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.09,0:02:42.72,Default,,0,0,0,,而且在我完事之后  这时雨应该就会停了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.68,0:02:45.68,Default,,0,0,0,,听说这雨会越下越大
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.77,0:02:47.60,Default,,0,0,0,,不知道明天操场还能不能用
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.44,0:02:51.56,Default,,0,0,0,,我没事  你不用在意
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.11,0:02:54.02,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然我似乎是偏火属性
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.07,0:02:56.82,Default,,0,0,0,,所以可能会被人怀疑雨是我的弱点属性
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.03,0:02:59.07,Default,,0,0,0,,不看我这样  其实我水属性也挺不错的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.15,0:03:01.36,Default,,0,0,0,,不  我从来都没有担心过这个方面
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.20,0:03:08.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs52.5\b0\bord0\shad0\c&H404040&\frz331.6\pos(1254,607.5)}这样子啊~~
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.20,0:03:08.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs52.5\b0\bord0\shad0\c&H404040&\frz329.7\pos(769.5,751.5)}师傅、一起回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.37,0:03:08.00,Default,,0,0,0,,可蕾说和我一起回去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.45,0:03:10.37,Default,,0,0,0,,是吗  真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.50,0:03:12.29,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯  谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.96,0:03:18.88,Default,,0,0,0,,可蕾
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.88,0:03:21.22,Default,,0,0,0,,宇佐美学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.93,0:03:24.55,Default,,0,0,0,,我买了河童雨衣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.76,0:03:26.10,Default,,0,0,0,,这颜色真好看
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.18,0:03:27.01,Default,,0,0,0,,对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.18,0:03:28.64,Default,,0,0,0,,伊万莉在等你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.06,0:03:31.06,Default,,0,0,0,,那我得抓紧了  再见
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.31,0:03:32.27,Default,,0,0,0,,拜拜
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.82,0:03:36.73,Default,,0,0,0,,河童?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.78,0:03:41.74,Default,,0,0,0,,今天是你值日吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.20,0:03:44.70,Default,,0,0,0,,算是吧  内卷要回去了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.12,0:03:45.58,Default,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.83,0:03:49.04,Default,,0,0,0,,要我帮忙吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.37,0:03:50.91,Default,,0,0,0,,不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.75,0:03:54.29,Default,,0,0,0,,内卷你有带伞吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.29,0:03:56.04,Default,,0,0,0,,有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.30,0:03:59.59,Default,,0,0,0,,那你带伊万莉一起撑回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.09,0:04:01.97,Default,,0,0,0,,她没有带伞  非常头疼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.72,0:04:06.01,Default,,0,0,0,,她现在应该还在楼梯口那里
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.35,0:04:10.27,Default,,0,0,0,,这倒也是  这么大雨
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.14,0:04:12.85,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.09,0:04:48.14,Default,,0,0,0,,武田老师
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.76,0:04:50.97,Default,,0,0,0,,收上来的笔记本我就放在这里了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.68,0:04:52.85,Default,,0,0,0,,宇佐美  麻烦你了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.27,0:04:54.31,Default,,0,0,0,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.56,0:04:56.15,Default,,0,0,0,,你要喝咖啡吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.73,0:05:00.32,Default,,0,0,0,,不用了  我还要收拾一下东西  就先走了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.65,0:05:04.20,Default,,0,0,0,,是吗  那能麻烦你帮忙补充一下粉笔吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.32,0:05:04.65,Default,,0,0,0,,什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.78,0:05:08.62,Default,,0,0,0,,就在器材室右边那个架子上
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.66,0:05:11.08,Default,,0,0,0,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.50,0:05:16.04,Default,,0,0,0,,我告辞了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.92,0:05:20.17,Default,,0,0,0,,看来还要花点时间
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.21,0:05:24.63,Default,,0,0,0,,瑞瑞  瑞瑞
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.76,0:05:25.42,Default,,0,0,0,,是薰吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.55,0:05:28.68,Default,,0,0,0,,其实我今天差点迟到  所以忘记带伞了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.76,0:05:29.64,Default,,0,0,0,,人家很可怜吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.68,0:05:30.72,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎么好意思说
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.39,0:05:37.40,Default,,0,0,0,,所以  瑞瑞你的伞我就借走了哇~
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.69,0:05:39.44,Default,,0,0,0,,给我等等
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.73,0:05:41.77,Default,,0,0,0,,别随便给我拿走
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.65,0:05:45.28,Default,,0,0,0,,原谅我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.36,0:05:46.36,Default,,0,0,0,,不  我这绝对不能原谅
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.65,0:05:48.24,Default,,0,0,0,,薰!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.49,0:05:56.21,Default,,0,0,0,,感觉祸不单行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.03,0:06:30.41,Default,,0,0,0,,薰那家伙  居然真带走了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.88,0:06:44.09,Default,,0,0,0,,你终于来了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.01,0:06:49.05,Default,,0,0,0,,内卷?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.64,0:06:51.51,Default,,0,0,0,,伊万莉呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.01,0:06:54.43,Default,,0,0,0,,这个的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.89,0:06:59.19,Comment,,0,0,0,,伊万莉同学
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.60,0:06:59.27,Default,,0,0,0,,那之后我马上来到这里找她  可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.02,0:07:03.27,Default,,0,0,0,,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.11,0:07:05.94,Default,,0,0,0,,伊万莉同学  你在做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.36,0:07:07.49,Default,,0,0,0,,伊万莉同学?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.15,0:07:10.49,Default,,0,0,0,,这是雨水
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.78,0:07:15.37,Default,,0,0,0,,亦或是泪水呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.92,0:07:27.25,Default,,0,0,0,,亚尔希安战记第二章  是和马莉安娜诀别的场景
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.42,0:07:28.09,Default,,0,0,0,,正确
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.01,0:07:30.80,Default,,0,0,0,,才不对  你这样会感冒的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.88,0:07:32.26,Default,,0,0,0,,内卷  你可别小瞧我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.43,0:07:37.97,Default,,0,0,0,,我可是有水之精灵的加护
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.14,0:07:38.93,Default,,0,0,0,,伊万莉同学
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.43,0:07:40.89,Default,,0,0,0,,伊万莉同学!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.56,0:07:44.19,Default,,0,0,0,,师傅  等等我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.23,0:07:45.52,Default,,0,0,0,,可蕾特同学  原来你也在啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.98,0:07:46.86,Default,,0,0,0,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.78,0:07:52.07,Default,,0,0,0,,就是这种情况
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.70,0:07:55.62,Default,,0,0,0,,真像那两个人会搞出的事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.12,0:07:59.50,Default,,0,0,0,,然后为什么你会留下来呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.58,0:08:02.71,Default,,0,0,0,,当然是在等你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.04,0:08:06.67,Default,,0,0,0,,你朋友把你的伞借走了不是吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.21,0:08:09.30,Default,,0,0,0,,瑞瑞就交给你了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.01,0:08:12.13,Default,,0,0,0,,内卷
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.02,0:08:23.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\b0\bord0\shad0\c&H453A38&\move(462,310.5,522,340.5)}薰
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.94,0:08:26.15,Default,,0,0,0,,薰
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.44,0:08:28.27,Default,,0,0,0,,要和我一起用这把伞吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.90,0:08:30.53,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯…嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.40,0:08:35.24,Default,,0,0,0,,薰  谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.41,0:08:38.12,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.04,0:08:42.08,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.08,0:08:44.08,Default,,0,0,0,,呃…没什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.96,0:08:45.58,Default,,0,0,0,,请吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.84,0:08:54.38,Default,,0,0,0,,打…打扰了…
